  - `:base` — the base config map (default `%{}`).
  - `:name` — optional GenServer name.
  - `:list_strategy` — `:replace` (default) or `:append`, global list merge strategy.
  - `:list_strategies` — a map of `key_path => :replace | :append` (paths as lists or
